\intbl 
{\ri30 \li30 
{\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \ql \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 
}
}
}\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ri30 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \ql \li30 \fs20 \intbl \cell \intbl 
{\ri30 \li30 
{\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \ql \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf31 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Issue of whether circuit court lacked subject matter jurisdiction could be considered by reviewing court even though appellant did not specifically raise it on appeal, where appellant consistently argued that lower court erred in granting partial summary judgment when only question set for hearing before court was appellant\rquote s motion to dismiss appellee\rquote s complaint on ground that appellee had sought judicial relief before exhausting its administrative remedies.
\par 
}
}
}
