}\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \ql \li0 \fs20 \intbl \cell \intbl 
{\ri0 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Section 29\u8211\'3f88, Gainesville Zoning Code, states in pertinent part:
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
No site plan shall be approved unless and until the board has made findings that the plan will meet the following criteria:
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
(a) Enhance and protect the public health, safety and welfare;
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
(b) Result in the least possible detrimental impact to the site and surrounding areas and not reduce the safety, light or general convenience of neighboring developments;
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
(c) Assure safe and convenient ingress to and egress from the property and internal circulation, including access of service and emergency vehicles and design of off-street parking and loading areas;
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
(d) Provide safe location and orderly arrangements and spacing of all buildings and structures;
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
(e) Minimize environmental damages caused by needless destruction of natural vegetation and natural features on the site....
\par 
}
}
}
}
}
}\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \qj \li200 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 \intbl \cell \row }
