3
}\super \b0 \cf33 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 }}
\par 
}
}
}\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \ql \li0 \fs20 \intbl \cell \intbl 
{\ri0 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Since the Plan Board gave final site plan approval with modifications, the Plan Board directed appellee to submit a revised set of plans and make all modifications within 60 days, or the site plan approval would become void.
\par 
}
}
}
}
}\b0 \cf1 \f3 \ri0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \qj \li0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 \intbl \cell \row }
